The highly anticipated BET Awards 2019 held last night at the Microsoft Theatre in Los Angeles. The exclusive event which celebrated Africans, African Americans and other American minorities in music, acting, sports, and other fields of entertainment featured live music performances, the awards ceremony and celebrity appearances all in one night. As expected the red carpet was filled with dazzling looks from the best of the best in the industry. From Mary J Blige’s Grecian look to Ciara‘s head-turning drape dress, keep scrolling to see our top 10 best looks at the event. *** LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA – JUNE 23: Ciara attends the 2019 BET Awards on June 23, 2019 in Los Angeles, California. (Photo by Frazer Harrison/Getty Images) Wearing Jean Paul Gaultier  LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA – JUNE 23: Karrueche Tran attends the 2019 BET Awards on June 23, 2019 in Los Angeles, California. (Photo by Frazer Harrison/Getty Images)  LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA – JUNE 23: Taraji P. Henson poses in the press room at the 2019 BET Awards at Microsoft Theater on June 23, 2019 in Los Angeles, California. (Photo by Liliane Lathan/Getty Images for BET) Wearing Balmain  LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA – JUNE 23: Mary J. Blige attends the 2019 BET Awards on June 23, 2019 in Los Angeles, California. (Photo by Aaron J. Thornton/Getty Images for BET) Wearing Alberta Ferretti  LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA – JUNE 23: Nomzamo Mbatha attends the 2019 BET Awards at Microsoft Theater on June 23, 2019 in Los Angeles, California. (Photo by Paras Griffin/VMN19/Getty Images for BET) Wearing Loin Cloth  LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA – JUNE 23: Yara Shahidi attends the 2019 BET Awards on June 23, 2019 in Los Angeles, California. (Photo by Frazer Harrison/Getty Images) Wearing Prabal Gurung  LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA – JUNE 23: Lizzo attends the 2019 BET Awards at Microsoft Theater on June 23, 2019 in Los Angeles, California. (Photo by Paras Griffin/VMN19/Getty Images for BET) Wearing House of Holland  LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA – JUNE 2